text: AOC can mean: * AOC International *Age of consent for sexual relationships * Air Operations Center - United States Air Force command and control (C2) system * Albanian Orthodox Church * Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez (born 1989), American politician * Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain (born 1993), English footballer * Appellation d'Origine Contrôlée, a certification for French agricultural products * Army Ordnance Corps, the predecessor of the Royal Army Ordnance Corps (RAOC) of the British Army * Articles of Confederation
